@startuml Communication Diagram - Auto-Tagging Feature
!theme cerulean-outline

title SmartMedia - Communication Diagram (Auto-Tagging Collaboration)

object scanner as "ScannerWorker"
object inferenceEngine as "InferenceEngine\n(Qwen2-VL)"
object dbController as "DatabaseController"
object vectorStore as "VectorStore\n(FAISS/Embeddings)"
object fileSystem as "FileSystem"

scanner -- inferenceEngine: 1. pass image\npath
scanner -- dbController: 2. query existing\nrecord

scanner -- inferenceEngine: 3. request AI\nprocessing
inferenceEngine -- vectorStore: 4. pass caption\nfor embedding

inferenceEngine -- scanner: 5. return\ntags + metadata

scanner -- dbController: 6. pass tags,\ncaption, objects

dbController -- fileSystem: 7. save thumbnail\nto disk

scanner -- vectorStore: 8. add vector\nto index

dbController -- fileSystem: 9. commit\nto database

vectorStore -- dbController: 10. confirm\nindex updated

note on link from scanner to inferenceEngine: Model inference\n~2 sec

note on link from inferenceEngine to vectorStore: Generate embedding\n~50ms

note on link from inferenceEngine to scanner: Extract metadata\n~10ms

note on link from scanner to dbController: Insert/update\n~5ms

note on link from dbController to fileSystem: Write thumbnail\n~20ms

note on link from scanner to vectorStore: Add 1536-dim\nvector\n~2ms

note on link from dbController to fileSystem: SQL commit\n~5ms

note on link from vectorStore to dbController: Finish\n~1ms

---

cloud "Auto-Tagging Workflow" {
  [scanner]
  [inferenceEngine]
  [dbController]
  [vectorStore]
  [fileSystem]
}

---

component [Auto-Tagging Pipeline] {
  interface [Input] as inp <<provided>>
  interface [Output] as outp <<provided>>
  
  inp : file_path : string
  outp : database_record : ImageRecord
  
  interface [Cache] as cache <<required>>
  interface [GPU] as gpu <<required>>
}

[Input] -- scanner: provides file

[Auto-Tagging Pipeline] -- [Output]: produces tagged record

[Auto-Tagging Pipeline] -- cache: accesses model cache
[Auto-Tagging Pipeline] -- gpu: uses GPU acceleration

---

note right of scanner
  **Scanner Responsibilities:**
  • Traverse file system
  • Load image/video/audio
  • Call inference engine
  • Pass results to DB
  • Track progress
  
  Triggers: Every ~2 sec
  Duration: Varies by file
end note

note right of inferenceEngine
  **Inference Engine:**
  • Load model (cached)
  • Resize image
  • Forward pass
  • Extract embeddings
  • Parse output text
  
  Model: Qwen2-VL-2B
  Device: GPU/CPU
end note

note right of dbController
  **Database Controller:**
  • Check if exists
  • INSERT or UPDATE
  • Manage transactions
  • Handle constraints
  • Commit to disk
  
  Driver: better-sqlite3
  Pattern: D-DAO
end note

note right of vectorStore
  **Vector Store:**
  • Load FAISS index
  • Add embedding
  • Update id_map
  • Persist to disk
  • Handle serialization
  
  Format: FAISS binary
  Dimension: 1536
end note

note right of fileSystem
  **File System:**
  • Save thumbnails
  • Manage paths
  • Handle cleanup
  • Permissions
  • Disk I/O
  
  Location: data/thumbnails/
  Format: JPEG
end note

---

partition "Message Flow Details" {
  
  note
    **1: Pass image path**
    From: ScannerWorker
    To: InferenceEngine
    Data: {path: string, media_type: str}
    
    **2: Query existing record**
    From: ScannerWorker
    To: DatabaseController
    Data: {path: str, id: str}
    Return: {exists: bool, record: null|ImageRecord}
    
    **3: Request AI processing**
    From: ScannerWorker
    To: InferenceEngine
    Data: {image_path: str}
    
    **4: Pass caption for embedding**
    From: InferenceEngine
    To: VectorStore
    Data: {text: str, media_id: str}
    
    **5: Return tags + metadata**
    From: InferenceEngine
    To: ScannerWorker
    Data: {caption: str, emotion: str, objects: List, scene: str, embedding: ndarray[1536]}
    
    **6: Pass tags, caption, objects**
    From: ScannerWorker
    To: DatabaseController
    Data: {id: str, caption: str, tags: List, objects: List, emotion: str, metadata: JSON}
    
    **7: Save thumbnail to disk**
    From: DatabaseController
    To: FileSystem
    Data: {image_data: bytes, path: str}
    
    **8: Add vector to index**
    From: ScannerWorker
    To: VectorStore
    Data: {id: str, vector: ndarray[1536]}
    
    **9: Commit to database**
    From: DatabaseController
    To: FileSystem
    Data: {transaction: begin/commit/rollback}
    
    **10: Confirm index updated**
    From: VectorStore
    To: DatabaseController
    Data: {success: bool, vector_count: int}
  end note
}

---

partition "Concurrency Model" {
  note
    **Thread Safety:**
    • ScannerWorker: main thread
    • InferenceEngine: GPU thread (async)
    • DatabaseController: sync (better-sqlite3)
    • VectorStore: in-memory (thread-safe)
    • FileSystem: I/O thread (OS managed)
    
    **Synchronization:**
    • Locks on model loading
    • DB transactions atomic
    • FAISS not thread-safe (single update thread)
    • File system ops serialized
    
    **Bottlenecks:**
    1. Model inference (GPU)
    2. Database writes (I/O)
    3. Vector store updates (CPU)
  end note
}

@enduml
